   across three macro trends in marketing: (1) growth of the sharing
   economy, (2) digitization of goods and services, and (3) expansion of
   personal data. This psychological ownership framework generates future
   research opportunities and actionable marketing strategies for firms
   aiming to preserve the positive consequences of psychological ownership
   and navigate cases for which it is a liability.
